Display clear.
KernelInstaller fileInClassChunks: 'RecorzKernelClass: #KeywordReporter superclass: #Object instanceVariableNames: ''''
!
setLeft: leftValue right: rightValue
    ^leftValue + rightValue
!'.
KernelInstaller rememberObject: ((KernelInstaller classNamed: 'KeywordReporter') new) named: 'keywordReporter'.
Transcript show: 'KEYWORD'.
Transcript cr.
Transcript show: ((KernelInstaller objectNamed: 'keywordReporter') setLeft: 2 right: 4) printString.
